name: SkyQuest Aviation, LLC
about: SkyQuest Aviation, LLC, located at the Langley Regional Airport in Canada, has been proudly training new and experienced pilots since 2003. With over 15 years of combined experience, our modern training facility and first-class equipment ensure all your flight training needs are met. We offer a variety of programs from initial training to vocational career training, whether you're flying for fun or as a career. Our in-house examination facilities make it convenient for students to challenge their Flight Tests and Written Examinations without additional travel. Our commitment to excellence and customer satisfaction makes SkyQuest Aviation the ideal choice for aspiring pilots. Start your training now and join our tradition of excellence in aviation education.
